      "id": "overview",
      "title": "Role Overview",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "content": {
            "text": "Business Analyst interviews assess your ability to translate business needs into actionable requirements, analyze data for insights, and communicate effectively across stakeholders."
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "content": {
            "text": "**What interviewers assess:**\n\n- Requirements gathering and documentation\n- Data analysis and SQL skills\n- Problem-solving and critical thinking\n- Stakeholder communication\n- Process improvement abilities"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "format",
      "title": "Common Interview Format",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "content": {
            "text": "**Typical BA interview loop:**\n\n1. **Recruiter screen** (30 min)\n2. **Hiring manager screen** (60 min)\n3. **Onsite/Virtual loop** (3-4 hours):\n   - Case study/analytical exercise\n   - SQL or data analysis round\n   - Stakeholder scenario round\n   - Behavioral round"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "tip",
          "content": {
            "text": "Practice structuring ambiguous problems. BAs often get vague requestsâ€”show you can ask the right questions to clarify scope."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
